    Class Description
    ActivityHelper
    Each EditPart which will get a tooltip showing the corresponding source code & source code line numbers will use this class for fetching all information for the tooltip.
    FancyTooltip
    This class defines a tooltip that is used within our EditParts.
    GoDeeperContextMenuProvider
    This class sets the context menu entry "go deeper", according to the following rules:
    - Is the element the mouse points to, when the right mouse button was clicked an EditPart?
    GotoButton
    This class defines the behavior of the goto button (scroll viewport to the position of the corresponding step node and execute fade out-animation for highlighting the corresponding Step node).
    GoUpContextMenuProvider
    This class sets the context menu entry "go up".
